scripts.package: npm run pack-linux-ia32 && npm run pack-linux-x64 && npm run pack-win32-ia32 && npm run pack-win32-x64 && npm run pack-mac

releases.name: vmd v1.28.0
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Switch markdown parser from [marked](https://github.com/chjj/marked) to [remark](https://github.com/wooorm/remark)
- Add support for headings without a space after the `#` sequence for GitHub compatibility (#90)
- Render unicode Emoji (e.g. `😄 👍`) as images

releases.name: vmd v1.27.0
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Preserve window size and position (#89)
- Update to Electron v1.4.1

releases.name: vmd v1.26.4
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Fix passing arguments for non-packaged app (#88)

releases.name: vmd v1.26.3
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Correctly resolve the path to the GitHub markdown stylesheets (#87) 
- Fix the file path arguments for the packaged releases
- Upgrade GitHub markdown styles
- Upgrade markdown parser due to a vulnerability
- Update to Electron v1.3.2

releases.name: vmd v1.26.2
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Make vmd work when running the executable not from a terminal
- Slightly improved icon

releases.name: vmd v1.26.0
releases.body:
Changelog:
- Update to Electron v1.2.1
- Add a default view when not opening a file (#84)
